data.name: Nine Pillars of Yang Zing
data.desc: When a Spell/Trap Card, or monster effect, is activated, and you control a "Yang Zing" card: Negate the activation, and if you do, shuffle that card into the Deck, then destroy 1 other "Yang Zing" card you control.

card_sets.set_name: Ghosts From the Past: The 2nd Haunting
